Python module 'visa'

A Python package for support of the "Virtual Instrument Software
Architecture" (VISA), in order to control measurement devices and test
equipment via GPIB, RS232, Ethernet or USB. 

* Prerequisites:

- VISA (tested with NI-VISA 3.2, WinXP, from www.ni.com/visa)
- ctypes (tested with 0.9.2, 0.9.5)
- Python (tested with 2.3, 2.4)

* Installation:

unzip source distribution file

>python setup.py install

* Description

see examples in directory test. A detailed specification of VISA can
be found on http://www.ivifoundation.org/Downloads/Specifications.htm

